						               													<description>Poten is an educational and functional board game that will help you find your potential and even think about a new job.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Poten is a standalone expansion of Flip. While Flip help you to learn about your personalities, Poten help you to find jobs that suit your personalities. When you combine those two games together and play them, they will give you a great fun and clear view of your passion.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How To Play:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Draft six 'work cards'.&amp;#10;     Set five 'icon cards' on the table.&amp;#10;     One player becomes a narrator and the rest will play the guessers. &amp;#10;     The narrator selects two icon cards and place a job card next to each icon card.&amp;#10;     And talk about two jobs represented by each set of icon &amp;amp; work cards as if he or she is currently working in that field. &amp;#10;     The other players listen to the stories and vote a job that suits the narrator better with the O token and place the X token on the other job secretly. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The objective of the game is to achieve the most victory points by guessing the right jobs that go along well with other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
